## 2. FIX: BIP39 Wordlist (wordlist_en.h)

**Télécharger** la wordlist complète:
```bash
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bitcoin/bips/master/bip-0039/english.txt
```

**Puis générer** le header:
```python
with open('english.txt', 'r') as f:
    words = [line.strip() for line in f if line.strip()]

print('const char* const BIP39_WORDLIST[2048] = {')
for i, word in enumerate(words):
    if i % 4 == 0:
        print('    ', end='')
    print(f'"{word}", ', end='')
    if i % 4 == 3:
        print()
print('};')
```

