## 5. FIX: secp256k1 (SOLUTION ALTERNATIVE)

**Option A**: Utiliser micro-bitcoin (recommandé)

```bash
# Dans platformio.ini
lib_deps = 
    https://github.com/micro-bitcoin/uBitcoin.git
```

**Option B**: Utiliser libsecp256k1 embarqué d'Arduino-ESP32

```cpp
// Utiliser les fonctions crypto ESP32-IDF
#include <mbedtls/ecp.h>
#include <mbedtls/ecdsa.h>
#include <mbedtls/sha256.h>

// Wrapper pour secp256k1
bool ecdsa_sign(const uint8_t* privkey, const uint8_t* hash, uint8_t sig[64]) {
    mbedtls_ecdsa_context ctx;
    mbedtls_ecdsa_init(&ctx);
    
    mbedtls_ecp_group_load(&ctx.grp, MBEDTLS_ECP_DP_SECP256K1);
    mbedtls_mpi_read_binary(&ctx.d, privkey, 32);
    
    mbedtls_mpi r, s;
    mbedtls_mpi_init(&r);
    mbedtls_mpi_init(&s);
    
    mbedtls_ecdsa_sign(&ctx.grp, &r, &s, &ctx.d, hash, 32, 
                       mbedtls_ctr_drbg_random, &ctr_drbg_ctx);
    
    mbedtls_mpi_write_binary(&r, sig, 32);
    mbedtls_mpi_write_binary(&s, sig + 32, 32);
    
    mbedtls_mpi_free(&r);
    mbedtls_mpi_free(&s);
    mbedtls_ecdsa_free(&ctx);
    
    return true;
}
```

